oves the performance of the motor. At a rated power of 750W, the Maxfoot motor can output at least 1050W of power. There will be no security risks due to its high performance."}},"10685e72-7bce-414d-a88b-6612ab13ca43":{"type":"bicycleTabsBox","settings":{"bicycleTabs_tabTitle":"Wiring","bicycleTabs_contentImg":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/b8c3cf51eaa7c133e580771f7493ae04.jpg","bicycleTabs_contentHeader":"Hidden wiring","bicycleTabs_contentDesc":"The wiring of MF-23 is hidden wiring, hidden in the frame with a unique design. Make the overall appearance of the vehicle even more beautiful. At the same time, hidden wiring also greatly reduces the exposure of the wires and prevents the wires from being damaged due to external factors."}},"66ca36e2-e080-46ca-bd6f-e1d4e3758743":{"type":"bicycleTabsBox","settings":{"bicycleTabs_tabTitle":"Handlebar","bicycleTabs_contentImg":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_0508.jpg","bicycleTabs_contentHeader":"Thoughtful Big Curved Handlebar","bicycleTabs_contentDesc":"Curved Handlebar aluminum handlebars allow adjustment to support various arm lengths and a more laid back riding position. During riding, the curved handlebar allows the rider to ride in a comfortable position. you will not feel uncomfortable because of the sitting position even when traveling long distances."}},"e0cb2b88-62d1-4451-a9c4-46e8e71f8912":{"type":"bicycleTabsBox","settings":{"bicycleTabs_tabTitle":"Headlight & Taillight","bicycleTabs_contentImg":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_3950701c-f889-4ee6-8a28-51cd99b504b6.jpg","bicycleTabs_contentHeader":"Integrated Headlight and Taillight","bicycleTabs_contentDesc":"The integrated power supply headlight and taillight provide guarantee for safe riding all day long. The headlight angle can be adjusted according to actual riding conditions to meet the needs of different road conditions. In addition to being always on, the taillight also have a brake highlight function, which can alert vehicles behind you in advance when slowing down."}},"51280dc9-2d5a-431f-afee-175342a3df3c":{"type":"bicycleTabsBox","settings":{"bicycleTabs_tabTitle":"Seat bag","bicycleTabs_contentImg":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_0269.jpg","bicycleTabs_contentHeader":"Seat bag with Reflector","bicycleTabs_contentDesc":"The surface of the MF-23 seat bag has concave and convex patterns set according to ergonomics to reduce the rider's fatigue during riding.The rear of the seat bag is also equipped with a reflector, which can use the light from back to remind the car behind, which is another important safety guarantee in addition to the taillights."}}},"block_order":["5ce8995f-ab6d-4b5f-9091-7bd2e39bb82f","4eadd67e-5a09-4d0d-b869-5cb42e5e0f4d","10685e72-7bce-414d-a88b-6612ab13ca43","66ca36e2-e080-46ca-bd6f-e1d4e3758743","e0cb2b88-62d1-4451-a9c4-46e8e71f8912","51280dc9-2d5a-431f-afee-175342a3df3c"],"custom_css":["{padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 50px;}"],"settings":{}},"39c18929-bdba-4f82-ae73-fb63c8fb1bde":{"type":"accordion-module","blocks":{"template--14619006337106__39c18929-bdba-4f82-ae73-fb63c8fb1bde-slide-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"heading":"Electronics","item_heading_1":"Battery","item_content_1":"SAMSUNG 48V 20Ah Lithium Battery","item_heading_2":"Hub Motor","item_content_2":"750W Brushless Geared Hub Motor","item_heading_3":"Throttle","item_content_3":"Variable Speed Control - 1\/2 Twist Throttle","item_heading_4":"Display","item_content_4":"Maxfoot 5 Inch LCD Display With USB Port","item_heading_5":"Controller","item_content_5":"Maxfoot 25A Overall Waterproof Controller","item_heading_6":"Integrated Wiring","item_content_6":"Water-Resistant Connectors and Wiring Harness","item_heading_7":"Lights","item_content_7":"Integrated Head\/Rear Light","item_heading_8":"Torque","item_content_8":"85N.m","item_heading_9":"","item_content_9":"","item_heading_10":"","item_content_10":"","item_heading_11":"","item_content_11":"","item_heading_12":"","item_content_12":""}},"template--14619006337106__39c18929-bdba-4f82-ae73-fb6